Program: Outlook
Title: Working Conditions in the Arabian Gulf
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/p03kbs5t
Last Broadcast Date: Not available
Summer working conditions for construction migrant workers in the Arabian Gulf. Also, actress Daryl Hannah on her tree-top protest against the closure of an urban farm. The 10 year old Ghanaian boy who preaches to thousands every Sunday; An urban soundscape from the streets of London. Sisters Anne and Eve Karpf talk about their professional interests in human voice. Presenter: Frederick Dove. Show less